Uses of Package
handist.collections

  • Packages that use handist.collections 
    Package Description
    handist.collections
    Contains a number of collections with access / index of keys using long rather than int.
    handist.collections.dist
    Contains the classes handling distributed collections, data relocation, and load balancing facilities.
    handist.collections.glb
    Contains the routines of the Global Load Balancer for the Distributed Collection Library
  • Classes in handist.collections used by handist.collections 
    Class and Description
    Bag
    Container for user-defined types.
    Chunk
    Large collection that can contain objects mapped to long indices.
    ChunkedList
    Large collection containing multiple Chunks.
    FutureN
    FutureN receives a list of Future and waits for the termination of all the futures.
    LongRange
    Class LongRange describes an interval over long values.
    ParallelReceiver
    Interface representing the capability for an implementing class to receive objects of a certain type from multiple sources.
    RangedList
    Abstract class describing a list defined on long indices.
    RangedListIterator
    Iterator interface for collections based on long indices.
    RangedListView
    RangedListView provides an access to a Chunk restricted to a specific range.
